title: Recently made logo for Swedish hostel
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204502im_/http:/typophile.com/files/Nya_Skogsgarden_col_3701.jpg)

This font is used by a Swedish hostel/camping to whom I'm about to create an ad. However - they don't have their logo anywhere else except on a printed card.

The cards are recently made by an unknown creator.

Font: 

 Southland 

Solved By: 

 [Renko](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204502/http:/typophile.com/user/12000 "View user profile.")
